  "1753510": {
    "name": "Cavemen Tales Collector's Edition",
    "steam_appid": 1753510,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1753510/extras/6cda313a5cbfd7ab53e40c9e3d0f6989.avif?t=1765448999\" width=630 height=122 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Step into a vibrant prehistoric world with Cavemen Tales: Prehistoric Adventure. Join Sam and Crystal as they lead their tribe to a new home, navigating through dozens of exciting levels filled with challenges, hidden treasures, and intriguing characters.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this fun and colorful time management game you will explore, guide the tribe, build, gather resources, overcome obstacles along the way and enjoy the tale of family, friendship and courage!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >However, be aware not everyone really has honest intentions. There are people who only strive to power and wealth!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1753510/extras/01a7c28b6d8fda0a91ece096cd97ae59.avif?t=1765448999\" width=630 height=122 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎯 Dozens of levels packed with city building fun</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🏰 Build, upgrade, and defend your towns</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >⚡ Use powerful boosts &amp; unlock achievements</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎧 Intriguing narrative — a plot with twists and memorable characters.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🛠️ 3 difficulty levels – from relaxed exploration to true challenge.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >📴 Play completely offline — anytime, anywhere</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔒 No data collection — your privacy is safe</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🕹 Gameplay</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Click / Tap to gather resources, build houses, manage workers, and keep your people thriving as you progress through each level. Use boosts when things get tough — but the real reward is mastering strategy and efficiency!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎮 Play your way</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Expand, optimize, upgrade, and develop your settlements the way you like. Customizable challenge — Relaxed, Standard, and Extreme difficulty modes. Earn Achievements as you complete objectives and perfect your strategy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🌌 Immersive adventure</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The mix of colorful art, atmosphere, and story-rich progression paired with satisfying time-management and city-building mechanics. Whether you enjoy calm, casual resource gathering or intense strategic challenges — this game delivers both.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1753510/extras/702f8ac782f1feae6a88bfc08002104f.avif?t=1765448999\" width=630 height=630 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This COLLECTOR'S EDITION version contains some special features:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bonus levels with extended story-line </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Additional achievements </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Art Gallery </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Soundtrack  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1753510/extras/f0f44b820a2849beb2caeb81b6b73741.avif?t=1765448999\" width=630 height=122 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Help Sam and Crystal and their family to find a new home</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Explore the prehistoric era and meet peculiar characters</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Stop the bad guys from ruining tribe's happiness</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Dozens of exciting levels to master and hundreds of quests</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Find hidden treasures and win achievements</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 3 difficulty modes: relaxed, timed and extreme</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Step-by-step tutorials for beginners</p></li></ul>",
